   <text type="translation">
      <body>
         <pb facs="1870_06_08_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Eduard_Schellhass_Shanghai_ 1.tif" n="1"/>
         <p>per Tapanguyo<lb/>EDUARD SCHELLHASS &amp; Co.<lb/>HONGKONG &amp; SHANGHAE<lb/> Shanghai
                8th June 1870<lb/>Messrs. L. Kniffler + Co.<lb/>Nagasaki<lb/>We acknowledge receipt
                of your esteemed <lb/>letters from 14th April &amp; 28th May and give <lb/>you our
                profound thanks for the interesting <lb/>reports contained within. <lb/>We are using
                today’s occasion to send you <lb/>samples of blue cloth and can offer you the
                <lb/>various available lots as follows.<lb/>
            <table>
               <row>
                  <cell>No. 1.</cell>
                  <cell>in stock</cell>
                  <cell>ca. 80 items </cell>
                  <cell>65/66 cloth.</cell>
                  <cell>27/28 yds.</cell>
                  <cell>at Tls 1”-”</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>＂ 2</cell>
                  <cell>＂</cell>
                  <cell>＂ 120 ＂</cell>
                  <cell> 65/66 ＂</cell>
                  <cell>60pr23/24＂<lb/>60.27/28＂</cell>
                  <cell>at＂ 1„30.</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>＂ 3.</cell>
                  <cell>＂</cell>
                  <cell>unlimited</cell>
                  <cell>＂ ＂</cell>
                  <cell>28/29＂</cell>
                  <cell>at ＂ 1. 03.</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>＂ 4</cell>
                  <cell>＂</cell>
                  <cell>ca 120 items</cell>
                  <cell>＂ ＂</cell>
                  <cell>25/26＂</cell>
                  <cell>at ＂ 1. 03.</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>＂ 5.</cell>
                  <cell>＂</cell>
                  <cell>＂ 50 ＂</cell>
                  <cell>66/88 ＂</cell>
                  <cell>26/28 ＂</cell>
                  <cell>at ＂ 1. 80.</cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <lb/>It would please us if you could manage <lb/>to place some part of these lots
                <lb/>and we are looking forward to your <lb/>esteemed news in this regard. <lb/>In
                the business there is no activity at all <lb/>due to the high rate among Chinese (3½
                to 4% per mth).<lb/>Referring also to the latest Chamber of Commerce <lb/>report, we
                sign <lb/>Mex $ 76_.<lb/>London 6 m/52 Bk[?]6/0½c<lb/>Yours respectfully<lb/>(p.p.)
                Eduard Schellhass + Co<lb/>J.J. Clausen</p>
